<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<note
	xmlns="http://www.sos-berlin.com/schema/js7_job_documentation_v1.1"
	xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" 
	xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
	<p>valid values for file size are</p>
		<table class="explanation">
			<tr>
				<th>Value</th>
				<th>Description</th>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td>-1</td>
				<td>The value of the parameter has no effect and the parameter is not part of the filter.</td>
			</tr>
            <tr>
                <td>number</td>
                <td>the number indicates the size in bytes, for example 40 means 40 bytes.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>numberKB</td>
                <td>the number indicates the size in kilobytes.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>numberMB</td>
                <td>the number indicates the size in megabytes.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>numberGB</td>
                <td>the number indicates the size in gigabytes.</td>
            </tr>
		</table>
</note>
